{"tid":1010562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國情咨文】特朗普：中國多年竊取美國知識產權及職位財富　指會建成美墨邊境圍牆","createTime":"2019-02-06T05:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T09:06:51.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db536745e18917536f0d08ea4960d4a1ba8cf8e6","tid":1010562,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T05:31:55.000Z","msg":"【國情咨文】特朗普：中國多年竊取美國知識產權及職位財富　指會建成美墨邊境圍牆<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190206/s00005/1549425948706/%e3%80%90%e5%9c%8b%e6%83%85%e5%92%a8%e6%96%87%e3%80%91%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%a4%9a%e5%b9%b4%e7%ab%8a%e5%8f%96%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e7%9f%a5%e8%ad%98%e7%94%a2%e6%ac%8a%e5%8f%8a%e8%81%b7%e4%bd%8d%e8%b2%a1%e5%af%8c-%e6%8c%87%e6%9c%83%e5%bb%ba%e6%88%90%e7%be%8e%e5%a2%a8%e9%82%8a%e5%a2%83%e5%9c%8d%e7%89%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190206%2Fs00005%2F1549425948706%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%2583%2585%25e5%2592%25a8%25e6%2596%2587%25e3%2580%2591%25e7%2589%25b9%25e6%259c%2597%25e6%2599%25ae-%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%25a4%259a%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e7%25ab%258a%25e5%258f%2596%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e7%259f%25a5%25e8%25ad%2598%25e7%2594%25a2%25e6%25ac%258a%25e5%258f%258a%25e8%2581%25b7%25e4%25bd%258d%25e8%25b2%25a1%25e5%25af%258c-%25e6%258c%2587%25e6%259c%2583%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e6%2588%2590%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%25a2%25a8%25e9%2582%258a%25e5%25a2%2583%25e5%259c%258d%25e7%2589%2586&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTCrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=39c34c32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190206%2Fs00005%2F1549425948706%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%2583%2585%25e5%2592%25a8%25e6%2596%2587%25e3%2580%2591%25e7%2589%25b9%25e6%259c%2597%25e6%2599%25ae-%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%25a4%259a%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e7%25ab%258a%25e5%258f%2596%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e7%259f%25a5%25e8%25ad%2598%25e7%2594%25a2%25e6%25ac%258a%25e5%258f%258a%25e8%2581%25b7%25e4%25bd%258d%25e8%25b2%25a1%25e5%25af%258c-%25e6%258c%2587%25e6%259c%2583%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e6%2588%2590%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%25a2%25a8%25e9%2582%258a%25e5%25a2%2583%25e5%259c%258d%25e7%2589%2586&h=b9ed57ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190206/s00005/1549425948706/%e3%80%90%e5%9c%8b%e6%83%85%e5%92%a8%e6%96%87%e3%80%91%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%a4%9a%e5%b9%b4%e7%ab%8a%e5%8f%96%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e7%9f%a5%e8%ad%98%e7%94%a2%e6%ac%8a%e5%8f%8a%e8%81%b7%e4%bd%8d%e8%b2%a1%e5%af%8c-%e6%8c%87%e6%9c%83%e5%bb%ba%e6%88%90%e7%be%8e%e5%a2%a8%e9%82%8a%e5%a2%83%e5%9c%8d%e7%89%86</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普於當地時間周二（5日）晚上9時（香港時間今早10時）開始，在國會發表國情咨文，歷時1小時12分鐘。特朗普期間呼籲兩黨團結，抨擊「政治或荒謬的黨派調查」，並強調會建成邊境圍牆，又指正與中國達成新的貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n捲入「通俄門」調查的特朗普在講話中表示，美國正發生「經濟奇蹟」，但他抨擊阻止這奇蹟發生的是「愚蠢的戰爭、政治或荒謬的黨派調查」，並指若要有和平與法規，就不可有戰爭和調查，「我們國內必須團結起來，打敗國外的對手」。<br />\n<br />\n對於美墨邊境圍牆，特朗普指其政府向國會提交一項「常識性」建議，以結束南部邊境危機，建議包括人道主義援助、港口毒品檢測、堵塞販賣兒童漏洞及建造邊境圍牆等，「過去在這個房間裏（國會會議廳），大多數人都投票贊成建牆，但合適的牆從未建成」，強調「我會把它建成」。<br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰方面，特朗普稱中國多年竊取美國的知識產權，盜竊美國的職位和財富，「但我不怪責中國利用我們，我怪責我們以前的領導人允許這種諷刺的事發生」。他續說，非常尊重中國國家主席習近平，稱美國正與中國達成新的貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n(美國有線新聞網絡)"},{"pid":"188bb3f394a41257f40f217127137c11033b33f4","tid":1010562,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T05:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af377f357e2d92d320387e5f4e30621bdd456118","tid":1010562,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T07:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192b1abb700a2ac9deaa3278a64d6b195dfadc3e","tid":1010562,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20